sequenceDiagram
    participant KonfluxCI as Konflux CI<br/>(Hermetic Build)
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>Kubernetes API
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant NotebookCtrl as ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Mutating Webhook
    participant KubeRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant Workbench as Workbench Pod<br/>8888/8787 TCP
    participant Nginx as nginx proxy<br/>80/TCP (Code-Server/RStudio)
    participant HTTPD as httpd CGI<br/>8080/TCP
    participant Culler as Notebook Culler
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipelines<br/>8888/TCP
    participant Runtime as Runtime Image<br/>(Pipeline Step)

    Note over KonfluxCI,Registry: Flow 1: Workbench Image Deployment

    KonfluxCI->>KonfluxCI: Build hermetic image<br/>(no network, cachi2 deps)
    KonfluxCI->>Registry: Push image<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Service Account auth
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Deploy ImageStream<br/>Kustomize manifests<br/>TLS 1.2+, ServiceAccount
    K8sAPI->>Registry: Resolve image digest<br/>HTTPS/443, Pull Secret
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: List ImageStreams<br/>HTTPS/6443, Bearer Token
    Dashboard->>Dashboard: Read opendatahub.io/*<br/>annotations for UI

    Note over Dashboard,Workbench: User creates workbench

    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR
    NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Mutating webhook intercepts
    NotebookCtrl->>NotebookCtrl: Resolve image from ImageStream<br/>Inject kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>Mount CA bundles + pipeline config

    Note over Culler,HTTPD: Flow 2: Idle Culling (Code-Server / RStudio)

    Culler->>KubeRBAC: GET /api/kernels/<br/>HTTPS/8443, Bearer Token
    KubeRBAC->>Nginx: Forward to nginx<br/>HTTP/80, localhost
    Nginx->>HTTPD: Proxy to CGI gateway<br/>HTTP/8080, localhost
    HTTPD->>HTTPD: Execute access.cgi
    alt Code-Server
        HTTPD->>Workbench: GET /codeserver/healthz<br/>HTTP/8787, localhost
        Workbench-->>HTTPD: Heartbeat response
    else RStudio
        HTTPD->>Nginx: Read access log<br/>File read
        Nginx-->>HTTPD: Last activity timestamp
    end
    HTTPD-->>Nginx: Jupyter kernel format JSON
    Nginx-->>KubeRBAC: Response
    KubeRBAC-->>Culler: Kernel activity status

    Note over Workbench,Runtime: Flow 3: Elyra Pipeline Execution

    Workbench->>DSP: Submit pipeline<br/>HTTP/8888, Bearer Token<br/>(in-cluster, no TLS)
    DSP->>Runtime: Launch runtime pod<br/>Pod creation, ServiceAccount
    Runtime->>Runtime: Execute notebook cells
    Runtime-->>DSP: Pipeline step complete
